159 (a) There is established the position of chief resilience officer who shall be the
160 administrative head of the office.
161 (b) The chairperson of the board shall nominate a chief resilience officer, subject to
162 approval by the board.
163 (c) The chairperson of the board shall establish the salary of the chief resilience officer,
164 subject to approval by the board, and the salary of such officer shall be drawn from the
